{"word":"εἰσόκε","slug":"εἰσόκε","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>εἰσόκε</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>εἰς ὅ κε</el>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>until</i>, with <a href='S:subjunctive mood'>subj.</a>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, (in 3. 409, <el>ποιήσεται</el> is epic for <el>ποιήσηται</el>). <p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>so long as</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}